msg: This commit addresses OODT-340. The home.jsp now redirects to login if someone has not logged into the application. In addition, put a TODO in one of the service interfaces that used to redirect to login.jsp. Service should return a not authorized if someone has not logged in and not redirect. There will be a new Jira issue opened for this.
